NAME		cube.sphere
SYNTAX		cube.sphere <x> <y> <z> <diameter> [red green blue]
DESCRIPTION	Draw a sphere, centered at x,y,z with given diameter.
		If the optional red, green and blue arguments are provided
		then that colour is used, otherwise the current working
		colour is used.
RETURN VALUE	None
EXAMPLES	Draw a sphere with diameter 6 at 4,4,4
			cube.sphere 4 4 4 6
		Draw a blue sphere with diameter 8 at 3,3,3
			cube.sphere 3 3 3 8 0 0 63
SEE ALSO	cube.colour
